    title: 'What helps a Kenyan business rank on Google Maps',
    paragraphs: [
      'Google Maps ranking depends heavily on the strength of the Google Business Profile. Completeness matters. Category choice matters. Review volume, review freshness, and business responses matter. So does consistent name, address, and phone information across the profile and website. Even details like photo freshness, service descriptions, and profile activity can influence local trust.',
      'Website signals also play a supporting role. If your Google Business Profile links to a weak site, local landing pages are missing, or the contact details do not match, the profile has less support. Strong Maps performance usually comes from a connected system: a well-managed profile, a solid local website, good reviews, and clean business information.',
