      'Tupate Studio handles website SEO and local visibility together because that is how Kenyan buyers actually search. The work can include technical cleanup, on-page optimisation, service page targeting, Google Business Profile setup or improvement, local keyword mapping, citation consistency review, review guidance, and monthly reporting.',
