      'Once visibility improves, maintenance becomes important too, because rankings are easier to protect when forms keep working, pages stay fast, and technical issues do not pile up. That is why our <a href="/website-maintenance-services-kenya">website maintenance service</a> fits naturally after the SEO foundation is in place.',
    ],
  },
