      'That is also why <a href="/articles/local-seo-kenya">local SEO for Kenyan businesses</a> should be adapted by city and area, not copied blindly from general international advice.',
    ],
  },
  {
    title: 'Technical SEO issues that hurt both organic rankings and Maps trust',
    paragraphs: [
      'Technical neglect hurts both channels. Slow pages, broken forms, poor mobile usability, missing schema, and inconsistent contact information all weaken trust. When the site underperforms, Google gets weaker signals and customers get a worse experience.',
      'If your site needs a deeper cleanup, our article on <a href="/articles/technical-seo-audit-kenya">technical SEO audits in Kenya</a> explains the kinds of issues that commonly block growth.',
    ],
  },
];

